  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为边缘AI平台设计一个四层架构图，从物理硬件层一直到应用层。最底层我想叫\"CAPA FÍSICA\"，包含Kubernetes节点、NVIDIA Jetson和树莓派集群。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FÍSICA",
        "Kubernetes Nodes",
        "NVIDIA Jetson",
        "RPi Cluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，物理层用橙色系的填充。那第二层是编排层对吧？我看到Helm和Istio的图标，是不是要放在\"CAPA PLATAFORMA\"里面？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PLATAFORMA",
        "Helm",
        "Istio",
        "Docker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，平台层用绿色。Docker、Helm、Istio这三个是核心。Helm和Istio的图标在Flaticon上看起来有点像，你区分一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PLATAFORMA",
        "Docker",
        "Helm",
        "Istio"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，平台层画好了，绿色填充。接下来是服务层？我看到API REST、gRPC和Kafka。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SERVICIOS",
        "API REST",
        "gRPC",
        "Kafka"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "服务层用蓝色系，叫\"CAPA SERVICIOS\"。这里要注意gRPC和Helm的图标别搞混了，虽然都是6134开头的编号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SERVICIOS",
        "API REST",
        "gRPC",
        "Kafka"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我查一下，gRPC是6134/6134346，Helm也是6134/6134346？不对，Helm应该是另一个编号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "gRPC",
        "Helm"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说错了。Helm是6134/6134346，但gRPC应该换成888/888054？不对，那是Istio。让我重新确认：gRPC用6134/6134346，Helm也是6134/6134346？这不对，Helm应该用3601/3601624。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Helm",
        "gRPC",
        "Istio"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我修正一下：Helm是3601/3601624，Docker也是3601系列？不对，Docker是3601/3601624？让我再核对——Docker是3601/3601624，Helm是6134/6134346？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Docker",
        "Helm"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "停，我们理清楚：Docker用3601/3601624，Helm用6134/6134346，Istio用888/888054，gRPC也用6134/6134346？这样Helm和gRPC就冲突了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Docker",
        "Helm",
        "Istio",
        "gRPC"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "那gRPC换个图标？或者Helm和gRPC确实可以共用同一个图标编号？这在Flaticon上是可能的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Helm",
        "gRPC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，Helm和gRPC都用6134/6134346，它们都是配置/协议相关的。继续吧，应用层是\"CAPA APLICACIÓN\"，紫色系，包含Dashboard 3D、Diagnóstico IA和Telemetría。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APLICACIÓN",
        "Dashboard 3D",
        "Diagnóstico IA",
        "Telemetría"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "应用层画好了。现在需要连接各层的关系。物理层到平台层是什么关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
