      "elements_involved": [
        "FÍSICA",
        "PLATAFORMA",
        "SERVICIOS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，两条连线加上了。服务层到应用层呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SERVICIOS",
        "APLICACIÓN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "服务层\"Alimenta\"供给数据给应用层。然后关键来了：应用层要有一个\"Control\"控制回物理层，形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
